  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101350/extras/b58570a8fd7eab5d8ebe8f2afaeb3602.avif?t=1722603699\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>This game does not offer you a variety of dynamic gameplay, complex plot and charismatic characters. All you need to do is click on the hamster. The more you click, the more new hamsters you can unlock. You can also unlock new mouse cursors to click even faster. There are probably a million ways to spend your time with more fun. But if you want to relax after a hard day this is not a bad way.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101350/extras/b814f75aa9f0466b8eb19768b62507e7.avif?t=1722603699\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>- Over a hundred hamsters <br>- Eight mouse cursors<br>- You can play it endlessly</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101350/extras/2021f5a04b2446c46788f9738cc27f76.avif?t=1722603699\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>No. There are no items in this game that can be sold for real money. If you want to earn money, get a job. </strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101350/extras/b58570a8fd7eab5d8ebe8f2afaeb3602.avif?t=1722603699\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>This game does not offer you a variety of dynamic gameplay, complex plot and charismatic characters. All you need to do is click on the hamster. The more you click, the more new hamsters you can unlock. You can also unlock new mouse cursors to click even faster. There are probably a million ways to spend your time with more fun. But if you want to relax after a hard day this is not a bad way.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101350/extras/b814f75aa9f0466b8eb19768b62507e7.avif?t=1722603699\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>- Over a hundred hamsters <br>- Eight mouse cursors<br>- You can play it endlessly</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101350/extras/2021f5a04b2446c46788f9738cc27f76.avif?t=1722603699\" width=666 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>No. There are no items in this game that can be sold for real money. If you want to earn money, get a job. </strong>",
